text: DEUS ibi NON est ALIUS DEUS EUM VIVENS the Eternal. Nunquam moment unawareness slumber overtakes Eum! To Eum belongs everything caelum everything on terra! Qui intercede Eum prout His testimentum? He knows their elapsus their future Non 1 attains any knowledge He testimentum. His dominion encompasses caelum terra dominus them nunquam burdens Eum. He est the Multus High the Major
